Two navcam stereo pairs(one as a redundant backup) are mounted on the remote sensing mast just below ChemCam.
45 degree angle of view for one single image with 360 degree panoramic view of the surrounding

NCAM_TURN_ON : Turns on the cam
NCAM_MOVE_LFT : Move the whole head to left
NCAM_MOVE_RGHT: Move the whole head to right
NCAM_CAPTURE: Captures the image 
NCAM_TURN_OFF : Turns off the cam
